      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I'm confused. Why are you talking about goblins? I'm just trying to understand my legal risk here. Can you please give me a serious explanation without the metaphors? I need to know exactly how much money I could actually be on the hook for if a client sues me because of a breach.",
